{"tid":1404782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警：有人刻意打扮成附近居民製造事端","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T21:17:31.000Z","uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":463,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"9dabb46c82b1a93810de70020daeaa86e7877a26","tid":1404782,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:52.000Z","msg":"黃大仙及油尖旺昨晚發生激烈警民衝突，警察隊員佐級協會強烈譴責有關暴力及破壞行為，並形容暴徒是「害怕曝光與蟑螂無異」。<br />\n<br />\n協會聲明指出，從網上片段可見，有人刻意換衣服打扮成附近居民，在黃大仙製造事端及暴力衝擊警察，有人在尖沙咀將國旗拆下及拋到海面，掛上有宣揚港獨的旗幟，明目張膽侮辱國家及挑戰國家主權的行為。<br />\n<br />\n協會表示，有人開始肆意在人口稠密的鬧市縱火及使用汽油彈，一旦發生火災後果不堪設想，屬於非常嚴重的罪行，呼籲停止有關行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472431-20190804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472431-20190804.htm&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=770f4ae5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472431-20190804.htm&h=9b7a3137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472431-20190804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9ec6e20645236bdf5adc049e78299d68512f08d0","tid":1404782,"uid":176657,"like":316,"dislike":3,"score":313,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"扮你老母臭閪呀 你班仆街暴徒扮警察添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9eb2fdcf9fd4f04fee54a52c0e712596c945b2","tid":1404782,"uid":14494,"like":291,"dislike":1,"score":290,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"有警員換成黑衫扮示威者搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba998c2848616e22016256bd6715e3442bb8c33","tid":1404782,"uid":265036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c234e9